      applications. Currently, I'm a <strong>Senior Frontend Developer</strong> at
      <strong id="e2">Mercedes-Benz</strong>, where I develop innovative,
      user-friendly applications, working remotely from the beautiful <strong
        id="e3">Muizenberg</strong
      >, <strong>South Africa</strong>.
    </p>

    <p>
      I bring ideas to life using a suite of modern tools and technologies,
